<div id="pf4480" class="pf w4d h2fe" data-page-no="4480"><div class="pc pc4480 w4d h2fe"><div class="t m4e x27 h5 y2ef7 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON 11 September 9-15 </div><div class="t md1d x15 hf9 y2b9e ff1 fs3e fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">TheFinishing of </div><div class="t m165e x92 hf9 y244a ff1 fs3e fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God&apos;s Work </div><div class="t m695 x26 h5 y23e ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;And this gospel of the kingdom </div><div class="t m42f x27 h5 y3fb ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">shall be preached in all the world for a </div><div class="t meaa x27 h5 y1479 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">witness unto all nations; and then </div><div class="t m8b x27 h5 y88 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">shall the end come&quot; (Matt. 24:14). </div><div class="t mf5e x26 h35 yad ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The end cannot come until the </div><div class="t m182 x27 h35 yd6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">gospel has been &quot;preached in all the </div><div class="t m1452 x27 h35 yab4 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">world for a witness unto all nations&quot; </div><div class="t m1af x27 h35 y198 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Matt. 24:14). A series of events of </div><div class="t m853 x27 h35 y6ea ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">great magnitude will take place before </div><div class="t m1e3 x27 h35 y1d1 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the end: the shaking and reformation, </div><div class="t m971 x27 h35 y494 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the sealing, and the latter rain. </div><div class="t m5fc x27 h35 y3bc ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">According to the Bible and the spirit of </div><div class="t m2b2 x27 h35 y17a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">prophecy, along with all these things, </div><div class="t me5f x27 h35 y337 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and simultaneously with them, the </div><div class="t m1adf x27 h35 ya6f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">people of God will undertake their </div><div class="t m48b x27 h35 y849 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">evangelistic work with special strength </div><div class="t m49d x27 h35 y4cb ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and fervor. </div><div class="t m104c x18 h35 yba ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Under the powerful outpouring of </div><div class="t m8ca x27 h35 y1a20 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the latter rain multitudes will be </div><div class="t ma6b x27 h35 ye06 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">admonished, and everyone true of </div><div class="t m2ce x27 h35 y37c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">heart will accept the gospel invitation </div><div class="t m1745 x27 h35 y8e5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and will receive the seal of the living </div><div class="t m620 x11 h35 ye5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God. But many will refuse to accept </div><div class="t m595 x27 h35 y233 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the truth and will receive the mark of </div><div class="t m98 x11 h35 y75e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the beast , becoming enemies of God </div><div class="t mb96 x11 h35 y1396 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and of His people. </div><div class="t m5f7 x18 h35 yc3 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">As the investigative judgment ends </div><div class="t m876 x11 h35 y161 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">in the court of heaven, probation will </div><div class="t m145 x11 h35 y110 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">close for the living. At that moment the </div><div class="t m48e x11 h35 y72 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">time of trouble begins, as well as the </div><div class="t m192 x11 h35 y503 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">outpouring of the seven last plagues. </div><div class="t m7e0 x11 h35 y76 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Also the preaching of the gospel will </div><div class="t m128 x11 h35 yebd ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">have been completed according to the </div><div class="t m58b x11 h35 y36e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">many promises and prophecies of the </div><div class="t m20e x11 h35 y328 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Bible. After a short time of trouble the </div><div class="t m347 x11 h35 y3c4 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Lord will at last descend from heaven, </div><div class="t m7a6 x11 h35 y30 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">bringing to an end all sorrow, pain, </div><div class="t m7cb x11 h35 y880 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and un righteousness. </div><div class="t me61 x4a h35 y953 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God could have dispensed with </div><div class="t m2aa x11 h35 y35 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">human beings in proclaiming the </div><div class="t m65c x11 h35 ye1d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">truth. He could have used angels,  </div><div class="t m70e x56 h35 y227 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">who, with a swift flash of glory, could </div><div class="t me94 x56 h35 y3fb ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">have done the job in a very short time. </div><div class="t m2ab x56 h35 y5b1 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">But He reserved to men and women </div><div class="t m3dc x56 h35 y375 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">saved by His grace this honorable and </div><div class="t m54f x56 h35 y4d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">beautiful task because He wanted to </div><div class="t m416 x56 h35 y434 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">honor us by associating us with Him. </div><div class="t mb73 x56 h35 ye5b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Also He planned to let us enjoy the </div><div class="t m287 x56 h35 yab4 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">happiness of seeing souls saved by the </div><div class="t m84a x56 h35 y243 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">blood of Jesus. He implants in every </div><div class="t m161b x56 h35 y6ea ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">born-again Christian an impelling </div><div class="t m4a3 x56 h35 y1d0 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">desire to share his faith. </div><div class="t m148b x78 h35 y15fe ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;No sooner does one come to </div><div class="t m6a9 x56 h35 y3bc ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Christ than there is born inbis heart a </div><div class="t m295 x56 h35 y585 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">desire to make known to others what a </div><div class="t m85c x7 h35 y3f2 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">precious friend he has found in Jesus; </div><div class="t m7d3 x56 h35 y1f8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the saving and sanctifying truth cannot </div><div class="t m6de x7 h35 y849 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">be shut up in his heart.&quot;â€”Steps </div><div class="t md80 x19b h35 y849 ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to </div><div class="t m336 x56 h35 y301 ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Christ, </div><div class="t m297 xbf h35 y301 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">p. 78. </div><div class="t m9c0 x78 h35 y217 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">We are going to study in this lesson </div><div class="t mb14 x7 h35 y1a20 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the promises of a finished work, the </div><div class="t mae4 x7 h35 y269 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">kind of message that has to be given at </div><div class="t m4db x7 h35 y37c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">this time, the work that will be done by </div><div class="t m747 x7 h35 y2a5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the Holy Spirit using human </div><div class="t m2b5 x7 h35 y33d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">instrumentalities, and the two great </div><div class="t m603 x7 h35 y233 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">conditions needed to finiSh the work. </div><div class="t m14a x7 h5 y290 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DAILY HIGHLIGHTS </div><div class="t m23f x7 h5 y21c ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t mbc x9f h5 y21c ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Promises and Prophesies </div><div class="t m455 x9f h5 y161 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rev. 14:6-11) </div><div class="t m558 x7 h5 y252 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m82e x9f h5 y252 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">A Time for a Clear Message </div><div class="t m3a2 x9f h5 y1a8 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Isa. 60:1, 2) </div><div class="t mb7 x7 h5 y426 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m1bf x9f h5 y503 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">A Fast and Miraculous Work </div><div class="t mce x9f h5 y87f ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rom. 9:28) </div><div class="t m1ce x7 h5 yebd ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m9f6 x9f h5 y1695 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Latter Rain and the Finishing </div><div class="t ma8f x9f h5 y36e ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of God&apos;s Work </div><div class="t m2bb x9f h5 y328 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rev. 18:1-4) </div><div class="t m8a8 x7 h5 y277 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t mdd5 x9f h5 y560 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">First Necessary Condition: </div><div class="t md5 x9 h5 y31 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Consecration </div><div class="t m469 x9 h5 y880 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Joshua 3:5) </div><div class="t m2ef x7 h5 yf3 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t m9fc x9 h5 y953 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Second Necessary Condition: </div><div class="t m455 x9 h5 y35 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Witnessing </div><div class="t m6a6 x9 h5 ye1d ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Mark 16:15) </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
